01:07:03.820 --> 01:07:05.090
Everyone, get up quickly!

01:07:05.190 --> 01:07:07.689
The people outside have run away.

01:07:07.789 --> 01:07:09.860
<i>We have to hurry and go.</i>

01:07:09.960 --> 01:07:11.389
