01:16:48.340 --> 01:16:50.130
Jae Hyeok!

01:16:50.270 --> 01:16:51.930
Jae Hyeok!

01:16:52.069 --> 01:16:55.300
Jae Hyeok!

01:16:55.479 --> 01:16:58.810
Nurse! Nurse!

